===Bonus DVD===
The special edition of the album includes a DVD containing a 35-minute documentary directed by percussionist [[Shawn Crahan]] about the album's conception and recording, titled ''Nine: The Making of All Hope Is Gone''.<ref name="BonusDVD"/> The recording of parts of "Child of Burning Time", "Dead Memories", "Snuff", "Vendetta", "This Cold Black", "Psychosocial", and "Sulfur" appear in the documentary.<ref name="DVD Chapters">{{cite web |publisher= [[Amazon.de]] |title = All Hope Is Gone: (CD+DVD) (Doppel-CD) |url= http://www.amazon.de/All-Hope-Gone-Slipknot/dp/tracks/B001BKXUOQ/ref=dp_tracks_all_2#disc_2|accessdate = 2008-08-23}}</ref> Instrumental effects and garbled music by Crahan are also featured on the DVD.<ref name="DVD Chapters"/>

